headline: The Latest AI Selloff: Insurance Brokers
summary: Shares of insurers sank as much as 25% after web-based insurer Tuio said its AI app would give personal home insurance quotes and sell policies.

headline: 3 Services Stocks Worth Your Attention
summary: Business services providers play a critical role for enterprises, assisting them with everything from new hardware integrations to consulting and marketing. Furthermore, the demand for their offerings is rising as more clients outsource non-core functions, a trend that has enabled the industry to return 9.1% over the past six months, almost identical to the S&P 500.
